This portal operates on anarchist principles, granting individuals the freedom to express themselves without censorship. However, it is important to maintain a respectful environment. Offensive terminologies are allowed, but if used in response to differing opinions or humor, they will not be tolerated. Please treat fellow members with courtesy and be open to adapting to the needs of the group. Additionally, access is restricted to individuals aged 18 and over, only those who are 18+ may join.

The posting, sharing, or distribution of any material that is gore related, pedopornographic, sexually explicit or depicts animal abuse is strictly prohibited. Any violation of this rule will result in immediate disciplinary action.

Members are encouraged to use the respective categories designated for specific topics of discussion in order to maintain organization and clarity within the Sunset Club group. This will ensure that conversations remain on topic and easily accessible for all members.

